&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Joyent:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joyent is a leading cloud computing software and services company, dedicated to empowering businesses with innovative, high-performance infrastructure solutions. We foster a dynamic and collaborative environment where talent thrives, and contributions are valued.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
