&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide day-to-day procurement support, including obtaining quotes, managing the purchasing process, workflows, and invoicing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Processing of various purchasing requests, including, but not limited to, software subscriptions, hardware, telecommunications, professional services, office supplies, and facilities&lt;/li&gt;
